#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"A lightweight, long-lasting foundation that provides full coverage while "
"allowing your skin to breathe."
msgstr ""
"Un fond de teint léger et durable qui offre une couvrance complète tout en "
"laissant respirer la peau."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"A rejuvenating facial treatment designed to reduce wrinkles and fine lines, "
"leaving your skin looking fresh and youthful."
msgstr ""
"Un traitement du visage rajeunissant conçu pour réduire les rides et les "
"ridules, laissant votre peau fraîche et jeune."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"A revitalizing facial that uses vitamin C and natural extracts to enhance "
"radiance and even out skin tone."
msgstr ""
"Ce soin du visage revitalisant contient de la vitamine C et des extraits "
"naturels pour renforcer l'éclat de la peau et unifier le teint."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Anti-Aging Facial"
msgstr "Soin du visage anti-âge"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_call_to_action
msgid "Beauty without <br/>expression is boring"
msgstr "La beauté sans <br/>expression est monotone"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Brightening Facial"
msgstr "Soin du visage illuminateur"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_intro_pill
msgid "Confidence and<br/>Timeless Elegance"
msgstr "Assurance et<br/>élégance intemporelle"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"Deeply hydrating facial treatment that restores moisture and balances your "
"skin, perfect for dry or sensitive skin types."
msgstr ""
"Un soin du visage qui hydrate en profondeur, rétablit l'hydratation et "
"équilibre votre peau, parfait pour les peaux sèches ou sensibles."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_intro_pill
msgid "Discover our products"
msgstr "Découvrez nos produits"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_beauty.field_theme_utils__display_name
msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "Nom d'affichage"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"Enhance your natural beauty with our range of luxurious cosmetic services "
"and products. Expertly crafted for every skin type and style."
msgstr ""
"Mettez en valeur votre beauté naturelle grâce à notre gamme de services et "
"de produits cosmétiques de luxe. Conçus par des experts, ils conviennent à "
"tous les types de peau et à tous les styles."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_features_wall
msgid ""
"Explore our luxurious makeup selection, offering vibrant colors and long-"
"lasting formulas for a flawless look every day."
msgstr ""
"Explorez notre luxueuse sélection de maquillage, composée de couleurs "
"éclatantes et de formules longue durée pour un look impeccable tous les "
"jours."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_features_wall
msgid ""
"Find your signature scent with our exclusive range of perfumes, crafted to "
"leave a lasting impression all day long."
msgstr ""
"Trouvez votre parfum fétiche grâce à notre gamme exclusive de parfums, "
"conçus pour laisser une impression qui dure toute la journée."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_features_wall
msgid "Fragrances and Scents"
msgstr "Parfums et senteurs"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"High-quality mascara that adds volume and length to your lashes, with a "
"smudge-proof and long-lasting formula."
msgstr ""
"Un mascara de qualité supérieure qui donne du volume et de la longueur à vos "
"cils, avec une formule longue durée et résistante aux bavures."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Hydrating Facial"
msgstr "Soin du visage hydratant"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_beauty.field_theme_utils__id
msgid "ID"
msgstr "ID"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_call_to_action
msgid "Join us and enjoy the pleasure of caring for yourself."
msgstr "Rejoignez-nous et savourez le plaisir de prendre soin de vous."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Long-Lasting Foundation"
msgstr "Fond de teint longue tenue"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_features_wall
msgid "Natural Skincare Products"
msgstr "Des soins naturels pour la peau"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Our Beauty Collection"
msgstr "Notre collection de produits de beauté"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_features_wall
msgid "Premium Makeup Collection"
msgstr "Une collection de maquillage haut de gamme"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_features_wall
msgid ""
"Revitalize your skin with our range of organic, chemical-free skincare "
"products designed for all skin types."
msgstr ""
"Revitalisez votre peau grâce à notre gamme de produits de soins biologiques, "
"sans produits chimiques, conçus pour tous les types de peau."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"Richly pigmented matte lipstick available in various shades, providing a "
"bold, long-lasting finish without drying out your lips."
msgstr ""
"Un rouge à lèvres mat, richement pigmenté, disponible en différentes teintes "
"pour un fini audacieux et durable sans dessécher les lèvres."

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_beauty.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Thèmes utiles"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Velvet Matte Lipstick"
msgstr "Rouge à lèvres mat toucher velours"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Volumizing Mascara"
msgstr "Mascara volume"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "✽  Facial Treatments"
msgstr "✽  Soins du visage"

#. module: theme_beauty
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_beauty.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "✽  Makeup Products"
msgstr "✽  Produits de maquillage"
